data.description:
Beautiful home w new floors throughout. Upper Lvl has 2 bed, bath, frml dining. The custom kitchen incls many upgrades and will be the centerpiece of this home. This home has plenty of Pella & Anderson windows & Maint-free deck to enjoy views of the clean, treated, well-fed pond! The pond provides a tranquil, less congested backyard. New Appls inc. water htr, dshw, refg & whl home humidifier.
 
Lower lvl addition creates xl master w abundant closet space, built in dressers & shelves. Lower also incls. lg living rm, Add'l. bed & family rm. Perfect for multi-family living. Elec floorboard heat was added for some extra warmth if desired. Lower walks out to lg cement patio. The yard is fenced for privacy. In-ground sprinkler system & many perennials for a low maintenance yard. This home is located close to the cities in a larger suburb, but when you are in the backyard, the quiet will make you feel like you are in a rural setting. You will get the best of both worlds with this home!!!!
